NAME
       ratium - A Dumb Little NCurses ASCII Game

SYNOPSIS
       ratium

DESCRIPTION
       ratium is a dumb little game where you are a '@' and have survive in an ASCII world by defending yourself from various enemies, such as the super rat.  Collect items
       such as tins of spam, swords, and haggises to survive.

COMMANDS
       To quit game press ctrl-c, or press ctrl-z to suspend game and exit to shell where you can enter 'fg' to bring it back up.

   MOVEMENT
	      h Move player left.

	      j Move player down.

	      k Move player up.

	      l Move player right.

   PLAYER ACTIONS
	      g Get item under player.

	      o Open/close door.

	      i Open inventory menu.

   INVENTORY
	      i Exit from inventory menu.

	      g Use item, depending on item type you can eat it or equip it in hand.

	      d Drop item onto map.

ENTITIES
   HOSTILE
       Rat (r)
	      Deals 1 damage and has 6 heath. Drops rat meat when it dies

       Super Rat (R)
	      Deals 2 damage and has 8 heath. Drops rat meat when it dies

   PEACEFUL
       Gnu (r)
	      Has 6 heath. Drops gnu meat when it dies

